"{\"uid\": \"wdio.com-front-page-local-news-the-annual-special-olympics-torch-run-returns-to-duluth\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The annual Law Enforcement Torch Run for Special Olympics took place on Monday at 11am at the Priley Circle Area at City Hall.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, it's a fundraiser.\", \"from\": 128, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For Special Olympics Minnesota.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 173, \"end\": 182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999998926682623, \"rank\": 8.979136810226992e-08, \"text\": \"Minnesota\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It partners up with law enforcement across the state to bring a torch from different parts of the state down to the cities where the summer Special Olympics games will be held this weekend,\\\" said Jeremy O'Connor, police officer of the Duluth Police Department.\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duluth_MN-WI_Metropolitan_Area\", \"score\": 0.9999807495928327, \"rank\": 1.9212663783207238e-05, \"text\": \"Duluth\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duluth_MN-WI_Metropolitan_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duluth_MN-WI_Metropolitan_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\", \"score\": 0.48733596539682245, \"rank\": 0.6584380179503769, \"text\": \"Police Department\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Flame of Hope\\\" was paraded around the city by participants of the Special Olympics and local law enforcement.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [{\"be